girl like yourself

40:51.670 --> 40:52.630
might forget, you know.

40:52.740 --> 40:54.870
I couldn't forget you.

40:56.240 --> 40:57.210
That was a nice try.

40:57.310 --> 40:59.010
I'll see you Saturday, Ellen.

41:10.420 --> 41:12.190
You must miss your girls, being her.

41:12.290 --> 41:13.590
Uh, before I leave,

41:13.690 --> 41:16.360
they are sweetest they have ever been.

41:16.460 --> 41:18.460
Aha. And school?

41:18.560 --> 41:20.880
Both smarter than me. I can admit this.

41:20.960 --> 41:23.060
My Katya, she is serious.

41:28.600 --> 41:31.170
He was going for Chinese food
at a place called Hunan Taste.

41:31.270 --> 41:32.840
That's the only reason he was out there.

41:32.940 --> 41:34.910
N. Hadley. Blue eyes. 5'11".

41:35.010 --> 41:37.080
US Naval Observatory patch on his hat.

41:37.180 --> 41:38.280
Black uniform.

41:38.380 --> 41:39.780
I saw everything, Mom.

41:39.880 --> 41:41.580
I was a mile out of the zone,
like I'm supposed to be.

41:41.680 --> 41:43.050
Waiting for my next shift.

41:43.150 --> 41:45.020
Maybe I shouldn't have been reading.

41:45.120 --> 41:47.120
It's okay. It's not your fault.

41:47.220 --> 41:48.450
I'm sorry, Mom. Damn it!

41:48.560 --> 41:51.460
This is-- This is part of it.
This is what happens.

41:51.560 --> 41:52.760
You handled it well.

41:52.860 --> 41:54.790
He has my ID. With my picture.

41:54.900 --> 41:57.260
Fake name, fake address.

41:57.370 --> 41:58.500
You gave him a fake phone number.

41:58.600 --> 42:00.770
You remembered everything. Okay?

42:00.870 --> 42:03.170
He's a security guard at
the US Naval Observatory.

42:03.270 --> 42:06.040
He's not a police officer.
This isn't a big deal.

42:08.710 --> 42:10.680
I really want you to understand this.

42:10.780 --> 42:13.700
Under pressure, you kept your cover.

42:13.780 --> 42:16.210
You said and did all the right things.

42:16.320 --> 42:18.120
There's nothing to worry about.

42:20.920 --> 42:22.420
Thanks.

42:45.350 --> 42:47.710
I need you to drop me near
Wisconsin and Calvert.

42:47.810 --> 42:49.580
- Is she okay?
- Yeah.

42:50.880 --> 42:52.980
I like Julie, but I told
you when she came on,

42:53.090 --> 42:53.950
she's too young.

42:54.050 --> 42:56.190
I have a lot of faith in this one.

42:56.290 --> 42:57.490
Drive.

43:13.610 --> 43:15.340
Wait, stop here.

43:38.200 --> 43:40.360
Excuse me. Sir?

43:40.460 --> 43:41.700
Can I help you?

43:43.440 --> 43:45.200
Miss?

43:45.300 --> 43:48.040
Yeah, uh, do you have a light?

43:48.140 --> 43:50.640
Yeah. Somewhere.

44:55.380 --> 44:58.080
I always like DC this time of year.

45:00.050 --> 45:04.090
I prefer it when the
cherry blossoms are out.

45:09.360 --> 45:10.960
You sure you're good?

45:11.060 --> 45:13.330
I spent nine hours getting clean.

45:13.430 --> 45:15.370
They'd have to have the whole FBI on me

45:15.470 --> 45:17.870
for me to miss it.

45:17.970 --> 45:19.300
Okay.

45:21.240 --> 45:23.280
Arkady Ivanovich sent me.

45:23.380 --> 45:26.110
We need your help.

45:26.210 --> 45:27.350
We?

45:30.220 --> 45:33.890
The people... running the
organization right now,

45:33.990 --> 45:36.260
they have very...

45:36.360 --> 45:38.560
old-line view of things.

45:39.490 --> 45:42.990
Not interested in all the
changes that are happening.

45:43.100 --> 45:46.360
And Gorbachev doesn't have the
power to get rid of them.

45:48.030 --> 45:50.200
I'm out of it.

45:50.300 --> 45:51.500
He told me.

45:53.640 --> 45:56.270
I wouldn't be here except...

45:58.180 --> 46:00.720
some very powerful people

46:00.740 --> 46:02.550
are out there to get rid of Gorbachev.

46:02.650 --> 46:05.740
To stop all the good things

46:05.760 --> 46:08.250
that have been happening
lately in our country.

46:09.160 --> 46:13.020
Your wife had a meeting in Latin America

46:13.130 --> 46:16.390
with a general from the
Strategic Rocket Forces.

46:17.460 --> 46:19.130
Strange, right?

46:20.870 --> 46:23.830
No stranger than us meeting here.

46:25.640 --> 46:29.540
My wife just does her job.

46:29.640 --> 46:31.240
That's all she's ever done.

46:31.340 --> 46:33.210
She's good at it.

46:33.310 --> 46:34.240
I know.

46:34.350 --> 46:37.410
But it's possible that she is being used

46:37.520 --> 46:40.050
by the people who are...

46:40.150 --> 46:44.090
trying to stop all the progress
that we've been making.

46:48.760 --> 46:51.530
Or she is one of them.

46:58.070 --> 47:01.000
Everything is divided up.

47:02.570 --> 47:05.710
That's how Arkady Ivanovich
explained it to me.

47:07.580 --> 47:11.050
This summit, it could
be a turning point.

47:12.080 --> 47:15.580
We have a pretty good
idea where you stand.

47:15.690 --> 47:17.450
I'm not involved anymore.

47:17.560 --> 47:20.120
And this has nothing to do with me.

47:24.360 --> 47:26.930
We want you to find out
what your wife is doing

47:27.030 --> 47:28.560
and tell us.

47:30.070 --> 47:33.400
And if you have to--

47:33.500 --> 47:34.770
stop her.

47:40.140 --> 47:41.980
She's my wife.

47:46.120 --> 47:47.550
I understand.

47:54.860 --> 48:01.600
I left my wife and my
baby boy to be here.

48:01.700 --> 48:04.070
I don't have any immunity.

48:05.740 --> 48:08.470
If I'm arrested, I'm finished.

48:10.440 --> 48:15.080
If they catch me and send me back,

48:15.180 --> 48:17.340
I'll be shot.

48:19.720 --> 48:24.620
I'm here because the
future of our country

48:24.720 --> 48:26.890
is being decided right now.

48:27.820 --> 48:29.960
You know that.

48:32.130 --> 48:35.800
I'm sorry you have to make
some tough decisions, too.

48:38.500 --> 48:41.070
I'll wait to hear from you.

49:41.030 --> 49:44.030
There's all this crap in the
paper about the Summit--

49:44.130 --> 49:46.430
like we're the ones
standing in the way...

49:46.530 --> 49:48.830
You working on it?

49:51.870 --> 49:53.840
It would be good if they made a deal.

49:53.940 --> 49:55.810
Fewer weapons.

49:58.680 --> 50:00.880
Fewer weapons for us, not for them.

50:02.180 --> 50:05.140
They just want to use
these treaties as a cover

50:05.160 --> 50:06.520
so they can keep building
up their arsenal

50:06.620 --> 50:08.250
while we get rid of ours.

50:08.350 --> 50:10.190
That sound fair to you?

50:11.160 --> 50:12.820
What's going on with you?

50:15.700 --> 50:17.160
What do you mean?

50:17.260 --> 50:19.900
Elizabeth, look at you.

50:23.640 --> 50:25.540
You smell like cigarettes all the time.

50:25.640 --> 50:27.300
Your whole way of being seems off.

50:27.410 --> 50:29.920
These past few months,

50:29.980 --> 50:31.740
