getting worse and worse.

50:31.840 --> 50:35.510
Well, I'm busy, obviously.

50:36.510 --> 50:39.180
It is finally getting to you.

50:39.280 --> 50:40.780
After all these years.

50:42.050 --> 50:44.120
You're amazing--

50:44.220 --> 50:46.860
