50:48.490 --> 50:50.700
When you told me to
quit, you were right.

50:50.720 --> 50:51.880
It was the best thing I ever did.

50:51.900 --> 50:54.130
And I was thinking...

50:54.230 --> 50:55.400
I'm-- Look.

50:55.500 --> 50:57.570
I'm so tired right now.

50:57.770 --> 50:58.970
Work was...

50:59.070 --> 51:01.440
I-I know. I'm sorry.
Look, I-I just need to--

51:01.540 --> 51:02.940
I have to talk to you about something.

51:03.040 --> 51:06.610
Let's talk tomorrow. I'm--
Honestly, I'm just beat.

51:06.710 --> 51:09.210
I-I know how hard you're working.

51:09.310 --> 51:10.650
I'm not complaining.

51:10.750 --> 51:12.710
This summit is a big deal.

51:12.820 --> 51:14.220
There's a lot to do.

51:14.320 --> 51:16.280
Whatever it is you want to talk about,

51:16.300 --> 51:17.440
we can talk about tomorrow.

51:17.520 --> 51:20.260
Whether it's Henry or
your work, it can wait.

51:20.360 --> 51:22.760
It's not Henry. Today, I--

51:22.860 --> 51:23.730
Whatever it is,

51:23.830 --> 51:24.760
I have to figure out

51:24.840 --> 51:26.360
what the hell is going
on with the Summit

51:26.460 --> 51:27.980
and everything else right now.

51:28.160 --> 51:31.420
So, I know you love to talk,
but you don't have to sit here

51:31.440 --> 51:32.830
and wait for me 'til
1:00 in the morning.

51:32.940 --> 51:35.380
I know how tired you are,
but I need to talk to you.

51:35.500 --> 51:38.710
If you knew how tired I am, you
wouldn't still be talking.

51:38.810 --> 51:40.010
Elizabeth, this-- this job you're doing,

51:40.110 --> 51:42.540
